value: Breeding range not definitely known but the species is recorded either in summer or as a spring and fall migrant in southeastern Siberia from Lake Baikal to the Amur, south to northwestern Mongolia and Ussuriland, also in Korea and Japan. Winters in China south to the Yangtse Valley.
refer: Peter's Checklist of the Birds of the World

value: Siberia and nw Manchuria; winters to e China, Korea, and Japan
